			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: new bard ~ needs grouping advice<a name="33495"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 8 04 1:39 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>You only need to have the instrument equipped when the song completes its cast time, so hold your instrument on your pointer and swap it in place of your weapon while your casting your song then swap your weapon back in off times, practicing the timing on this will help get you in the groove for more intense type twisting later on for short spurts. 
<br />
Example
<br />
Start singing song 1 
<br />
Equip horn
<br />
Stop singing song 1 
<br />
Equip weapon
<br />
Start singing song 2
<br />
stop singing song 2
<br />
rinse repeat.. twist n shout! 
<br />

<br />
Just getting this timing down will make it easy for you to swap a instrument in for short bursts when you need to without fumbling over it. 
<br />
